Component.Description:
Continuously rotates an entity around the Y-axis. Useful for display
pedestals, collectibles, decorative elements, or loading indicators.

Usage:
  trophy.setComponent(Spinner(speed = 30f))  // 30 degrees per second

System implementation:
  class SpinnerSystem : SystemBase() {
    private val query = Query.where { has(Spinner.id, Transform.id) }
    override fun execute() {
      val dt = systemManager.getDeltaTime()
      for (entity in query.eval()) {
        val spin = entity.getComponent<Spinner>()
        val t = entity.getComponent<Transform>()
        val rotation = Quaternion.fromAxisAngle(Vector3(0f, 1f, 0f), spin.speed * dt)
        entity.setComponent(t.copy(pose = t.pose.rotate(rotation)))
      }
    }
  }

Attributes:
  - speed: Rotation speed in degrees per second (default 50.0)
